Page_0:
"By the Builder! I can hear the bell ringing!
Lord Raglan is still alive!"
page_0_color: "#DDBAAB"
page_0_time: "9s"

Page_1:
"My vow is fulfilled! I kept watch over thy grave, and as thou hadst
feared, thou wert buried alive. But now thou art free, and so am I."
page_1_color: "#DDBAAB"
page_1_time: "14s"

Page_2:
"Please accept my rosary beads as my way of saying thank thee."
page_2_color: "#DDBAAB"
page_2_time: "7s"